{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Wed\u322?ug Johna N. Jonesa{\super\chftn}{\*\footnote\chftn\~\plain\pard {\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 J.N. Jones, {\i Sculpting God: The Logic of Dionysian Negative Theology}, ,,Harvard Theological Review\u8221", vol. 89 (1996), ss.\u160?355\u8211-371.\par}
